0c-9f29-420c-b412-2b6ffb85d95c">Giana Darling</a>, <a class="hover:text-cyan-700 dark:hover:text-cyan-500" href="/authors/3d5468df-86f2-47c3-ad34-e7dcc4aebef4">Emma Hart</a>, <a class="hover:text-cyan-700 dark:hover:text-cyan-500" href="/authors/1900192f-b440-4b25-8224-b422af19126f">Chelle Bliss</a>, <a class="hover:text-cyan-700 dark:hover:text-cyan-500" href="/authors/fa25f02e-70df-47f2-9d42-a05a736897f2">Noelle Adams</a>, <a class="hover:text-cyan-700 dark:hover:text-cyan-500" href="/authors/7b348bcf-711c-49dc-a3db-28eaa3d9a16d">A. Zavarelli</a>, <a class="hover:text-cyan-700 dark:hover:text-cyan-500" href="/authors/f84bbdd8-ddd9-4d52-b6b7-6f4d1b9677b3">Jenika Snow</a>, <a class="hover:text-cyan-700 dark:hover:text-cyan-500" href="/authors/f68d99f5-b910-4be4-a40b-63a118edf21f">Dylan Allen</a>, <a class="hover:text-cyan-700 dark:hover:text-cyan-500" href="/authors/a0777c67-2378-4299-a99c-afa53f8f8f03">Audrey Carlan</a>, <a class="hover:text-cyan-700 dark:hover:text-cyan-500" href="/authors/4252b0e8-bfea-4f76-874a-f5c56ab5954c">Robin Covington</a>, <a class="hover:text-cyan-700 dark:hover:text-cyan-500" href="/authors/bf7debc2-d5d3-491d-be5a-b06d72ef45e6">Mary Catherine Gebhard</a>, <a class="hover:text-cyan-700 dark:hover:text-cyan-500" href="/authors/d1e24155-e032-4b35-990e-95270fa1e145">Melanie Moreland</a>, <a class="hover:text-cyan-700 dark:hover:text-cyan-500" href="/authors/eaffaadd-d332-4bb5-b9f3-e46db2c37cea">Parker S. Huntington</a>, <a class="hover:text-cyan-700 dark:hover:text-cyan-500" href="/authors/2692ee06-6531-4e19-a970-72e75d898938">Nana Malone</a>, <a class="hover:text-cyan-700 dark:hover:text-cyan-500" href="/authors/5216a994-3c38-45d5-b767-9cffdcca09fc">Jewel E. Ann</a>, <a class="hover:text-cyan-700 dark:hover:text-cyan-500" href="/authors/626f5ca2-a6b0-40dd-b3b6-f8d1ebda9865">Annabel Joseph</a>, <a class="hover:text-cyan-700 dark:hover:text-cyan-500" href="/authors/bc2cb023-9eb5-41a2-8bf4-3c1d94deacf6">Celia Aaron</a>, <a class="hover:text-cy